name: John Morris
description: I am a man of my word. I do what I say or I don’t say it. I am also a man who gives what he gets. If you give me unconditional love, I will do my best to return it. If you give me confrontation, I will return it as well, and I hate confrontation. Although I played baseball, basketball and hocky when I was young, I really enjoy golf now. My passion has always been music. I play in an old time rock and roll band on weekends when we can get work. I still get paid, but I do it for fun now. I am also interested in sports cars
